<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>As it has not been possible to collect payment for your policy, we regretfully inform you that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">your insurance policy has been cancelled from inception</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. This is in accordance with our Terms and Conditions.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please be advised that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">your insurance is now considered null and void and you have no rights to any cover</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. Claims made on this policy will not be honoured.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>If you have any questions then please do not hesitate to get in touch. We hope you will considered Kingsbridge for your business insurance in the future.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
